{"tid":674794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東華學院物理治療課程未獲審批","createTime":"2018-05-23T04:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T12:23:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"457956ad7bd76f1595d2d4c327fe145d02e58dc2","tid":674794,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:19:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180523/20398959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180523%2F20398959&d=9hIK144lkxzBKkv7H8CMvcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f153ce2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180523%2F20398959&h=baf1002b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180523/20398959</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月23日 <br />\n<br />\n東華學院物理治療課程未獲審批<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180523/large/23la8p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180523%2Flarge%2F23la8p4.jpg&h=3bb0e629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葉建源<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】東華學院擬今年9月開設4年制自資物理治療學士學位課程，課程需經審批才獲專業認可。但教育界立法會議員葉建源指，專業評審委員會仍未成立，專業認證準則亦無公開，憂慮報讀課程的學生未能取得專業認證。翻查資料，負責成立評審委員會的「物理治療師管理委員會」，過去5年平均每年開會1次，有一年更全年無開會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學生恐難取專業認證<br />\n<br />\n葉建源指，專業評審需時甚長，評審委員會查詢師資、師生比例、教學方法等。他憂慮課程有機會不獲專業認可，「你未經歷認證，學生入嚟讀有風險，但無學生讀又認證唔到喎」。他認為應先做初步評審，確立清晰評審準則，有助學院申請專業評審，令學生畢業後獲認可的執業資格。<br />\n<br />\n「物理治療起動」發言人列明慧指，涉事課程9月已開學，據悉學院亦已聘請老師和提交申請資料，但專業評審仍遙遙無期，形容情況荒謬。她批評，物理治療師管理委員會成員全數由政府委任，對業界無問責性，一年平均只開一次會，無法解決業界積壓已久問題。<br />\n<br />\n物理治療師管理委員會成員李偉志指，院校有提供資料，但委員會未實質收到專業評審的申請。他指委員會一直有為申請作準備，惟不便透露進度。他又解釋，委員會是按需要開會。記者昨向東華學院查詢申請進度，截稿前未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n■記者潘柏林  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n馬路窄多欄杆　恐殃及途人<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n機電署研強制換舊𨋢"},{"pid":"6e86b317b66e54bbb100cefa5098fd01ca28c0cd","tid":674794,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"咁啫係讀完等於冇讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de8f00051d031501065ce1cd968802f313f71eb","tid":674794,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac4e2dffb3ff8b5f7f09e146c2f2a16f17e5b28","tid":674794,"uid":134988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:26:31.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac02660ab5e27e78b0d2f25b0ec754ac123966f","tid":674794,"uid":53554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:27:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50d1c56396071d1a5dd5381a0f52c71ef82ba701","tid":674794,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:42:12.000Z","msg":"讀完執唔到葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fff64d31e0e9aac47902c62913e5a04ea2d721","tid":674794,"uid":9781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T12:15:29.000Z","msg":"之前職業治療課程都係咁,最後唔知係咪夾住班學生先拎到牌<br />\n依家又想用返同一招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75abb64b6556dc72241d8222cc55c94e2bced017","tid":674794,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2fff64d31e0e9aac47902c62913e5a04ea2d721","tid":674794,"uid":9781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T12:15:29.000Z","msg":"之前職業治療課程都係咁,最後唔知係咪夾住班學